                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="Modal2" class="modal fade" role="dialog">
                    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">

                        <!-- Modal content-->
                        <div class="modal-content">
                            <div class="modal-header">
                                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">&times;</button>
                                <h4 class="modal-title">Move host javi.net to new server</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-body">
                                <div class="box-body">
                                    <div class="shortInfoContainer">
                                        <div class="col-sm-3 shortInfo">
                                            <h4>Date opened</h4>
                                            7/8/2016 11:23:00
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-3 shortInfo">
                                            <h4>Department</h4>
                                            Technical support - Website Developer
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-2 shortInfo">
                                            <h4>Status</h4>
                                            Closed
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-sm-3 shortInfo">
                                            <h4>Last modified</h4>
                                            9/8/2016 11:23:00
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <hr />
                                    <div class="detailContainer">
                                        <div class="col-lg-12 detail">
                                            <h4>Ticket Description</h4>
                                            <p>I wish to change my website's main color to red. The color code is #ff3434. Please email me when my request is solved.</p>
